42:05.890 --> 42:05.889
Thank you, sir.

42:05.891 --> 42:09.559
You ready to learn some shit
they're never gonna teach you

42:09.561 --> 42:10.760
-in school?
-Yeah.

42:11.762 --> 42:13.696
No. Yes, sir.

42:13.698 --> 42:16.566
Treat me with the same respect
you treat your old daddy,
