42:17.535 --> 42:18.568
Yes, sir.

42:18.570 --> 42:20.703
Good man. Now hold that up.

42:22.039 --> 42:24.941
Now the thing is,
with these key holes,

42:24.943 --> 42:27.944
you can treat them nice
and kind and tell them lies

42:27.946 --> 42:29.879
and feed them candy
and all that shit.

42:29.881 --> 42:32.015
But sometimes it's just
not gonna cut it.

42:32.017 --> 42:34.918
Sometimes, like now,

42:34.920 --> 42:37.554
