be a stubborn old thing.

42:38.589 --> 42:39.789
Shit.

42:41.692 --> 42:42.725
Like your brother
over there.

42:44.295 --> 42:45.795
Sitting in the car.

42:45.797 --> 42:47.730
Watching us like a hawk.

42:47.732 --> 42:48.965
Hey, Donnie.

42:51.702 --> 42:52.902
Stubborn old thing.

42:53.237 --> 42:54.337
Anyway,

42:55.606 --> 42:58.908
trick to breaking
a bad pony here is,

42:58.910 --> 43:01.144
I am telling you, he's not
gonna give you what you want.

43:02.613 --> 43:05.715
Then you just have to...

43:05.717 --> 43:06.849
- Ram it home.

43:08.919 --> 43:10.086
Bingo.

43:11.589 --> 43:12.789
Dammit.

43:58.068 --> 44:00.236
-Carolyn Simmons?
-Who's asking?

44:00.238 --> 44:01.404
Arizona state police.

44:03.107 --> 44:05.241
-I am Carolyn.
-Yeah? You know this guy?

44:06.944 --> 44:06.943
What did Randy do?

44:06.945 --> 44:10.747
-You've seen him?
-A couple of weeks ago
up at the prison.

44:10.749 --> 44:13.082
-Nonsense.
-If you got
nothing else, mister,

44:13.084 --> 44:14.984
I got my papers to deliver.

44:14.986 --> 44:16.386
It's lieutenant, ma'am.

44:16.388 --> 44:17.754
You mind if I take
a look around?

44:25.396 --> 44:27.797
Password.
That's a good one.

44:32.670 --> 44:34.904
You deliver these papers
without reading them?

44:34.906 --> 44:36.673
You've seen his face
on the front page, huh?

44:36.675 --> 44:38.074
Just dear Abby
and the horoscopes.

44:40.678 --> 44:42.145
What's your relationship
with greenawalt?

44:42.147 --> 44:44.247
-"Relationship"?
-You visit him regular.

44:44.249 --> 44:46.883
Well, he was kinda my boy
when he got set up.

44:46.885 --> 44:48.785
Started writing me letters.

44:48.787 --> 44:51.454
-He wouldn't hurt nobody.
-Mm-hmm, yeah.

44:51.456 --> 44:53.856
Well, you hear from him,
i hear from you.

44:53.858 --> 44:54.824
You understand?

44:54.826 --> 44:56.826
Well, what should I tell him?

44:56.828 --> 44:57.994
Will he listen to you?

44:59.129 --> 45:00.363
I suspect so.

45:01.265 --> 45:02.432
Tell him to turn
himself in.

45:04.868 --> 45:05.868
You have a good one.

45:21.485 --> 45:23.252
What do you think?
Hard as she gets, yeah?

45:23.254 --> 45:24.721
Four by four, like you asked.

45:25.289 --> 45:26.723
It got no camper.

45:28.358 --> 45:29.892
It's solid.
It's a good truck, dad.

45:29.894 --> 45:30.927
Damn good truck.

45:32.196 --> 45:34.997
Now, how about we all of us
go sit in that truck?

45:37.334 --> 45:39.736
And put them
dime card punches away, boy.

45:39.738 --> 45:40.937
You know what's good for you.

45:47.778 --> 45:50.747
But you said your old lady
had a truck with a camper.

45:50.749 --> 45:52.515
Tell her you're at camp.

45:52.517 --> 45:54.484
It's going to be fine, Gary.

45:54.486 --> 45:56.352
Shit, just let the boys
ride in the back.

45:57.421 --> 46:00.189
I want ray upfront
with me and Ricky.

46:00.191 --> 46:02.325
Donnie, pull that seat
out of the Maverick
and ride back there

46:02.327 --> 46:03.526
