writing something
like this?

46:23.915 --> 46:26.215
You want to get people feeling
sorry for these animals?

46:26.217 --> 46:27.784
It's called an interview.

46:27.786 --> 46:29.519
Has she been in touch
with any of these boys?

46:29.521 --> 46:31.154
-No.
-"No"?

46:32.422 --> 46:33.956
