is a punishable offense.

46:39.497 --> 46:42.465
I expect you know this
is the usa, we have
a free press.

46:42.467 --> 46:44.500
Mm-hmm.

46:44.502 --> 46:46.903
I don't know what you're
playing here.

46:46.905 --> 46:48.337
