-No.

47:08.426 --> 47:09.525
Just thinking.

47:10.494 --> 47:13.062
Yeah. Me, too.

47:15.999 --> 47:18.000
I don't like
what they've done.

47:18.002 --> 47:20.136
They had no reason
killing anybody.

47:20.138 --> 47:23.039
I wasn't thinking nothing
against dad.

47:23.041 --> 47:24.440
I was just thinking
about Mexico.

47:30.948 --> 47:32.281
Who is keeping watch?

47:32.283 --> 47:33.349
