47:34.518 --> 47:35.852
What's Donnie doing here?

47:35.854 --> 47:37.320
Nothing, I just went
to take a piss,

47:37.322 --> 47:39.555
figured I'd keep ray company.

47:39.557 --> 47:43.359
No, I need you rested up.
You're driving tomorrow.

47:43.361 --> 47:46.596
