splitting off in commissary.
Understand?

47:47.231 --> 47:48.364
Just talk is all.

47:49.933 --> 47:53.302
Donnie said we got no reason
to kill that family.

47:58.475 --> 48:00.977
Listen to me.
I told you boys,

48:02.012 --> 48:03.512
what happened back there,

48:03.514 --> 48:05.114
it was Randy's idea.

48:07.317 --> 48:08.651
It's not the way
i wanted it to go.

48:09.486 --> 48:10.519
Yes, sir.

48:14.091 --> 48:16.292
You ever know me to hurt
anybody didn't ask for it?

48:17.895 --> 48:19.128
Is that the way
you were raised?

48:21.365 --> 48:23.966
You think I am some dog
that needs to be put down?

48:25.969 --> 48:27.236
No, sir.

48:27.238 --> 48:29.972
Then don't talk like I was.

48:29.974 --> 48:32.041
And don't poison your
brothers against me.

48:35.112 --> 48:36.145
Go.

48:44.054 --> 48:45.187
What else he say?

48:45.689 --> 48:46.989
Nothing, sir.

48:49.192 --> 48:50.526
You're doing a good job, ray.

48:52.930 --> 48:55.665
I think this whole thing
is gonna work out
because you are here.

48:56.967 --> 48:58.134
Thank you, sir.

49:06.243 --> 49:07.443
Stay alert.

49:09.179 --> 49:10.313
Stay awake.

49:14.551 --> 49:15.985
<i> I hear riders.</i>

49:27.965 --> 49:27.964
Hey.

49:27.966 --> 49:32.535
I tried calling, but all i
got was a busy signal.

49:32.537 --> 49:34.103
-Thank you.
-For what?

49:35.405 --> 49:37.006
That was a real
nice story you wrote.

49:37.008 --> 49:38.975
There are two sides
to every story.

49:38.977 --> 49:40.409
Your side needed
to be told.

49:40.411 --> 49:42.345
Come in, sit down.

49:49.987 --> 49:52.054
I got a call today.

49:52.056 --> 49:54.590
-Oh.
-Do you know
Mary Joe west?

49:55.525 --> 49:55.524
-On TV?
-Mm-hmm.

49:55.526 --> 49:59.295
Her people called me.
They want me to come
into the station tomorrow

49:59.297 --> 50:00.763
and do an interview.

50:00.765 --> 50:02.465
Do you want to?

50:02.467 --> 50:05.134
Well, there's a lot of people
who want to talk to me,

50:05.136 --> 50:06.602
and I expect I need
someone to help.

50:09.206 --> 50:10.573
-I'll call her.
-Good.

50:17.214 --> 50:19.015
You didn't hear
from anyone else?

50:19.017 --> 50:20.282
-Like who?
-The boys.

50:20.650 --> 50:22.084
Your husband.

50:22.086 --> 50:23.319
Don't you think I'd tell you?

50:25.055 --> 50:26.122
