50:47.645 --> 50:49.245
What the fuck
is she doing?

50:49.247 --> 50:51.080
Shut up, I am watching this.

50:51.082 --> 50:53.582
<i> So, your boys have</i>
<i> already spent</i>

50:53.584 --> 50:53.582
<i> a good deal of time</i>
<i> in prison.</i>

