<i> Are you proud</i>
<i> of your children?</i>

51:02.325 --> 51:04.226
<i> You don't have children,</i>
<i> do you, Mary Joe?</i>

51:04.228 --> 51:06.262
<i> May I call you Mary Joe?</i>

51:06.264 --> 51:07.530
Bitch should shut
her mouth.

51:07.532 --> 51:10.099
-Shush!
-They gave him
two life sentences.

51:10.101 --> 51:12.468
